{"tid":2077372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"DC佬遞交建議：市區DC落旗費由24蚊加到34蚊！！！","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:58:31.000Z","uid":10014,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1caada228a0ec81755c513920a3e91c328f32f12","tid":2077372,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:41:08.000Z","msg":"市區、新界以及大嶼山的士業界於2018年9月向運輸署提交加價申請，平均加幅達20.39%至25.71%不等，當中建議市區的士落旗收費由24元增至30元，即增6元，惟相關方案一直未有落實。<br />\n<br />\n最主要的士業商會近日向的士車主發出內部通告，擬修訂市區的士落旗起錶加價方案，上調6元至10元，即落旗加至30至34元，但每次跳錶維持不變，料7月最快達成共識並提交最新方案至運輸署。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲狠過房署"},{"pid":"02f24b5e143c4687947ac1673c24160ac57a04c5","tid":2077372,"uid":66945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:41:44.000Z","msg":"咁唔好再話佔中搞到冇生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615ec192a840f003e00dd34fe7570c908839f243","tid":2077372,"uid":185158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"你咪加，都無人搭"},{"pid":"255bb88fb75657a8932012103f65ca8ad1734f0a","tid":2077372,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"唔係想倒「黃的台」米，咁既價錢點幫得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58089d5253337450d72189c89671e35156bf722","tid":2077372,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂<br />\n咪少d人搭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763d4d4ef6286b9c846f025fc52239bada2c34ef","tid":2077372,"uid":81353,"like":1,"dislike":